  "texts": [
    "Specifically, the students yielded the highest satisfaction mean on scale items \"I am concerned about the privacy of my information when using ChatGPT\" (𝑥̅ =3.90; σ=0.969) and \"I am concerned about the potential risks to my data security when using ChatGPT\" (𝑥̅ =3.44; σ=0.939).",
    "This study wanted to determine differences in the level of satisfaction of nursing students on ChatGPT use based on the metrics the usefulness, ease of use, credibility, social influence, and privacy and security.",
